{"tid":150092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"生活實試 : 淘寶電單車「救命」背心 結果死兩次","createTime":"2017-03-09T18:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T02:09:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e33bad313407201d6ac1c8735f9d4ffdf5ae6285","tid":150092,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/ireserve-694x434.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fireserve-694x434.png&h=abc462b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一款電單車用的安全自動充氣背心，可以在司機出事前快速充氣減低撞擊力，不過在外國的售價在由幾千元起。小編看到淘寶有一款千多元的同類產品，平這麼多到底 OK 嗎 ? 今次我們就派叻姬姐姐試一下。<br />\n<br />\n 中國自家正貨賣 1130人仔<br />\n我們在淘寶找了這款充氣安全背心，內有 50cc 壓縮氣體，聲稱啟動後能於 0.5 秒內充滿，並擁有中國的專利權。聽下去好像很可信而且很便宜，所以 unwire 就買回來試試。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/TB-web-688x580.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2FTB-web-688x580.png&h=8064fbf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n扣子爛掉作用<br />\n這背心運作原理是這樣的，安全線一端扣在電單車上一端扣在背心。當司機被拋出電單車時，安全線會扯掉壓縮氣樽的安全扣，並且充氣保護司機。不過叻姬第一次測試時，一扯扣子就爛掉，人就飛出去，可是背心卻沒半點反應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/khjgkhkghk-1-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fkhjgkhkghk-1-694x390.jpg&h=3a31104a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成功充氣  但又漏氣<br />\n再次測試，今次成功讓背心充氣了。不過原來一邊充一邊漏氣，沒有突然「漲起」的感覺，只有漲起那麼一點點，今次測試結果是完全失敗，叻姬如果真的使用的話，應該死了兩遍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/jgkhjkg-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fjgkhjkg-694x390.jpg&h=c406ace8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 叻姬感想 : 不會買了<br />\n她指出就穿著感來說是不錯的，輕身而且通風。不過測試結果如此，假若她駕駛電單車就不會買了。小編覺得關乎到生命的產品，還是買一些大品牌比較安全。雖然淘寶便宜貨吸引，但自己生命無價。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/03/07/duhan/life-tech/auto/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2Fduhan%2Flife-tech%2Fauto%2F&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=67a05acd\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/03/07/duhan/life-tech/auto/</a>"},{"pid":"62895311a2c004a4189b242142c039e04ed7cfd9","tid":150092,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:37:49.000Z","msg":"我淨係驚果支充氣既野會唔會無情情爆炸啫？所以係三次"},{"pid":"b97864865c0a3dbf1fd4838a10755db2005c6d9a","tid":150092,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T19:11:23.000Z","msg":"想響淘寶淘自己條命翻黎? 唔係壞腦啊? 冇睇過死響意大利海灘上嘅難民所著嘅救生衣係邊度生產?<br />\n<br />\n【唔係中國製嘛！】黑心救生衣塞滿海棉 吸水下沉害死無數難民<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170211/56289629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170211%2F56289629&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=15ee19a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170211%2F56289629&h=764437d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170211/56289629</a>"},{"pid":"2c412fa4c82b51da9211dffe0b6627e546c0edb9","tid":150092,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T19:17:01.000Z","msg":"阿媽係女人，試黎都多鳩餘"},{"pid":"fbaa9044548796a7ed0e508a9f41c190e49a474f","tid":150092,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T19:55:33.000Z","msg":"淘寶<br />\n有名你叫"},{"pid":"82892027ebb9ab783e33fbf82fdc20762bc2d4c5","tid":150092,"uid":15903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T19:57:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想響淘寶淘自己條命翻黎? 唔係壞腦啊? 冇睇過死響意大利海灘上嘅難民所著嘅救生衣係邊度生產?<br />\n<br />\n【唔係中國製嘛！】黑心救生衣塞滿海棉 吸水下沉害死無數難民<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170211/56289629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.